@startuml

title Event-Driven Architecture
|Event Source|
start
:Emit event;
|Event Bus|
:Route event;
fork
  |Consumer A|
  :Handle in A;
  if (ack?) then (yes)
    :Acknowledge;
  else (no)
    :Dead letter;
  endif
fork again
  |Consumer B|
  :Handle in B;
  :Store result;
fork again
  |Consumer C|
  :Handle in C;
  :Notify users;
end fork
|Event Bus|
stop
@enduml
